{"tid":1846964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國國務院警告國民不要前往中國，考慮到武漢肺炎是一種致命冠狀病毒","createTime":"2020-01-27T21:07:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T09:38:55.000Z","uid":125193,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c427460a65c1aa6986f670813a7d33e7e55ff0e5","tid":1846964,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T21:07:34.000Z","msg":"美國國務院警告國民，不要前往中國，並表示，考慮到湖北武漢是一種致命冠狀病毒的起源地，呼籲國民不要前湖北省。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院表示，已經要求美國政府所有非緊急的工作人員和家屬撤離湖北，又表示美國政府在該省對其國民所能提供的緊急服務能力有限。聲明又表示，中國政府可能會在很短時間或沒有事前通知之下，實施旅遊限制，旅客要為此做好準備。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505178-20200128.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505178-20200128.htm&d=gjA94EiKSJsk9JMrtOnM5jvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=ae0fd391\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505178-20200128.htm&h=f54aeb01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505178-20200128.htm</a>"},{"pid":"92b9f3a5fc036803dd29346711211c49c559fda8","tid":1846964,"uid":104470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T21:10:36.000Z","msg":"嚴重漏洞！！微博教湖北佬走法律罅搭船嚟機場轉機播毒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1846852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1846852</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"515d69013a03597ec2be0bd50bab7d060a3ef224","tid":1846964,"uid":104470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T21:11:43.000Z","msg":"中國政府可能會在很短時間或沒有事前通知之下，實施旅遊限制，旅客要為此做好準備。<br />\n<br />\n幾時禁支那人嚟香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6a08511fe40743c1f1229854b0ee189ff6c8924","tid":1846964,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T21:11:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fa